data.title: Dennis Rogers on LinkedIn: Usher Announces ‘Past Present Future Tour,’ Including Shows At Intuit Dome
data.meta_description: Just getting started! Usher becomes first artist to announce concerts at Intuit Dome with shows Sept. 21 and 22. Grand Opening in…
data.text:
The Halo Board reveal was a major success...one more step closer to our opening show on August 15th https://lnkd.in/g3vENurZ

The objective was to collect every high school jersey across California, totaling over 1550! It was an ambitious goal, but with the support of an exceptional team, we achieved it. I want to extend my gratitude to Chris Wallace Justin Dunn Kevin Lam Matthew Leiva I am extremely proud of this accomplishment, and it will undoubtedly be a highly celebrated addition to Intuit Dome. https://lnkd.in/gYqQcHmC

Great rollout across many media outlets of our innovative ticketing plan, the "Ultimate Wall Pass." Appreciate Front Office Sports for this one.

Excited this announcement is out, August 15th will be here very soon! https://lnkd.in/g3HMGQU4

An incredible event yesterday announcing that our G League team will relocate to Oceanside, CA and rebrand as the San Diego Clippers, playing in the brand new Frontwave Arena This was a fun one to plan and execute. https://lnkd.in/gsr34KqY

Years of planning came to fruition this week as we unveiled our new uniforms, logo, and brand look while we prepare to move into our new home, Intuit Dome, next season. Proud to play a small part in it. https://lnkd.in/gSS5qDRG

An incredible event this week to officially announce the 2026 NBA All-Star Game will take place at Intuit Dome. More than 1 billion impressions over broadcast and social media resulted from the event. Intuit Dome becomes the first arena still under construction awarded the game. https://lnkd.in/gUucSQPU
